channel.title: Dellscape Preview Video
channel.description:
Ok To start it off, i will have maybe bout 5 previews...
[i][b]1. (realeased April 29th, 12:49pm eastern time) - Preview Of Full Specials On Npcs[/b][/i] Video: [URL=http://video.tinypic.com/player.php?v=43ra993]Dellscape Video - Full Specials On Npcs, Including D2h special, Darklight special, Granite maul special, Excalibur special, a little glitchy and my daughter was screaming at start, other than that enjoy :)[/URL]
^^ If That Doesnt Work - Go Directly To The Website ^^
Video: http://video.tinypic.com/player.php?v=43ra993
[i][b]2. (realeasing April 30th, 5:00pm eastern time) - Preview of full specials on players..[/b][/i] Video: Coming soon
[i][b]3.(realeasing may 3rd, 5:00pm eastern time) - Preview Of Full Pest control (not really, cant get portals to spawn npcs, and spinners wont heal portals)[/b][/i] Video: Coming Soon
[i][b]4.(releasing May 6th, 5:00pm eastern time) - Preview Of all defenders except Mithrial defender[/b][/i] Video: Coming Soon
[i][b]5. Dellscape Source And Client Release (Releasing May 10th)[/b][/i] Client: - Webclient: - Source: -
Im Really sorry if any of these videos are low quality, its only because im using my unregistured hypercam, and it records nonsence things, only the specials on npcs will be the most anooying other than that enjoy.
[size=10pt]Please Feel Free to post your comments or conserns[/size]
From, You friendly neighboorhood hero, Dell :)
